imdb.plot outline: Pablo Herminio loves being a bodyguard. When he rescues Antonia, a magnate in the flower industry, she offers him a full time position as her personal bodyguard. Pablo soon learns that working for Antonia involves a lot of personal sacrifice and could cost him the love of his life...a young doctor named Maia who happens to be the daughter of Antonia's worst enemy and business rival.
